<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會<delay20 />已經開始了喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要不要來數數看放了幾發煙火呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可別像在數羊一樣，數著數著就睡著囉。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火<delay8 />真是漂亮呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我覺得煙火發射時的聲響很大、很嚇人，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但也正因有如此魄力，所以才能打動人心吧。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />我問你喔。<delay frames="40" />
你不覺得綻放在夜空中的高空煙火，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實和人很像嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管煙火有著什麼顏色或形狀，<delay8 />
都有其獨特的特點，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每個都很有魅力喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經拍過照了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟這煙火美到讓人忍不住
想用照片記錄下來呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過果然煙火還是要親眼觀賞，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能看到最美麗的樣子，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火不論在什麼時候欣賞<delay8 />
都如此令人陶醉呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果有人在跟我求婚時，
用100發高空煙火代替100朵玫瑰的花束，<delay8 />
我也會感到很高興呢。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />感覺大家都看煙火看得很入神呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能夠看到大家這麼快樂的表情，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也覺得很開心喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />討厭，<delay20 />我的臉上黏了什麼東西嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為你突然一直盯著我看<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />你說我的眼裡倒映著煙火？<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />就算我今天看起來比平常漂亮，<delay8 />
你也別像這樣一直盯著我看嘛。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會害羞的<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />活動已經接近尾聲了。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快樂的時光總是過得特別快呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然有些令人不捨，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但還是讓我們一起享受到最後吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">能夠欣賞美麗煙火的美好時光
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也所剩不多了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />美好的時光終有結束的一刻，<delay8 />太感傷了。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛才的煙火很美對吧～<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />害我一時激動，做出了不符合年齡的行動呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼？<delay20 />你問我的年齡？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們已經說好不問這個問題了吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>